dcterms:creator: P. Central
dcterms:description: A dataset for bar chart detection, collected from article PDFs in the PubMed Central Open Access Subset, containing 1592 document page images with manually labeled bounding boxes for each bar chart.
dcterms:title: Bar chart detection

dcterms:creator: X. Liu
D. Klabjan
P. NBless
dcterms:description: A dataset of synthetic bar charts generated for value detection, containing 5000 charts with varying numbers of bars and values, used for pre-training.
dcterms:title: Synthetic bar charts for value detection

dcterms:description: A dataset of manually annotated real chart values, containing 500 vertical-only bar charts sampled from the bar chart detection dataset, with precise labeling of bar, tick, and origin points.
dcterms:title: Manually annotated real charts values

dcterms:creator: X. Liu
D. Klabjan
P. NBless
dcterms:description: A dataset of real-augmented synthetic charts, created by augmenting synthetic bar charts with real chart surroundings to improve local feature learning.
dcterms:title: Real-augmented synthetic charts

dcterms:creator: X. Liu
D. Klabjan
P. NBless
dcterms:description: A dataset of synthetic pie charts generated to demonstrate the extensibility of the method, containing point annotations for the boundaries between pie wedges and the pie chart centroid.
dcterms:title: Synthetic pie charts
